    .column.xlarge-6
      h3 Bitcoin Split
      p Many merchants choose to take a percentage of their settlement in bitcoin. This can be done by taking a Bitcoin Split. You can choose to take any percentage&mdash; or all of it&mdash; in bitcoin.
      p You can set up a bitcoin split in your #[a(href="https://bitpay.com/dashboard/settings/settlement") Settlement Settings]. Settlement is paid daily to your bitcoin address on file.

    .column.xlarge-6
      h3 Exchange Rates
      p Merchants who generate invoices in a currency different from their settlement currency will receive the exchange rate as calculated at the time the invoice was generated, using the rates provided by #[a(href="https://openexchangerates.org/") openexchangerates.org].
